FT  11 JUN 93 / UK Company News: Losses deepen to Pounds 2.98m at Welpac
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Welpac, the hardware and electrical goods wholesaler, reported a pre-tax
deficit of Pounds 2.98m on turnover of Pounds 17.1m in the year to January
31.
That compared with a loss of Pounds 694,000 from sales of Pounds 9.72m for
